1
00:00:11,205 --> 00:00:12,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

2
00:00:14,605 --> 00:00:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

3
00:00:18,905 --> 00:00:21,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong? You're soaking wet.</font>

4
00:00:22,939 --> 00:00:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

5
00:00:26,305 --> 00:00:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What happened to you?</font>

6
00:00:27,705 --> 00:00:29,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

7
00:00:30,205 --> 00:00:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm getting a divorce.</font>

8
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So... what is it this time?</font>

9
00:00:42,872 --> 00:00:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Probably just another fight
with my brother over something stupid.</font>

10
00:00:47,772 --> 00:00:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Something like he didn't notice
you changed your hair,</font>

11
00:00:50,505 --> 00:00:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">or he ate some fried chicken
you were saving for yourself.</font>

12
00:00:53,405 --> 00:00:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They've always fought over dumb stuff.</font>

13
00:00:56,405 --> 00:00:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a waste of time to worry about them.</font>

14
00:00:59,939 --> 00:01:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Nao,</font>

15
00:01:01,572 --> 00:01:03,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry,
but can I stay here for a while?</font>

16
00:01:05,705 --> 00:01:08,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure, of course. That's fine.</font>

17
00:01:08,105 --> 00:01:09,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

18
00:01:09,072 --> 00:01:11,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey. This is my house too, you know.</font>

19
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please, may I?</font>

20
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:21,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the heck happened between you?</font>

21
00:01:24,505 --> 00:01:25,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya...</font>

22
00:01:26,805 --> 00:01:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's been...</font>

23
00:01:28,905 --> 00:01:30,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">having an affair.</font>

24
00:01:30,305 --> 00:01:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Really?</font>

25
00:01:32,205 --> 00:01:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way in hell my brother--</font>

26
00:01:34,305 --> 00:01:37,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes he has! That's why...</font>

27
00:01:39,205 --> 00:01:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm getting a divorce.</font>

28
00:01:43,405 --> 00:01:44,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

29
00:01:48,939 --> 00:01:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to talk with my brother.
I'll sleep over there tonight.</font>

30
00:01:54,605 --> 00:01:55,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

31
00:01:56,205 --> 00:02:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Take care of Yuri for me.
-OK, I will.</font>

32
00:02:02,472 --> 00:02:04,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here.
-Thanks.</font>

33
00:02:04,205 --> 00:02:05,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take care.</font>

34
00:02:07,305 --> 00:02:11,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't believe this. An affair?
Totally impossible.</font>

35
00:02:11,939 --> 00:02:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That brother of mine
would never have an affair.</font>

36
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's hot!</font>

37
00:02:32,705 --> 00:02:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really can't believe... That's hot!</font>

38
00:02:35,205 --> 00:02:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...that he had an affair.</font>

39
00:02:37,705 --> 00:02:40,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder
if Yuri really is going to get a divorce.</font>

40
00:02:42,505 --> 00:02:44,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on a second.</font>

41
00:02:44,505 --> 00:02:47,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If that really does happen...</font>

42
00:02:48,205 --> 00:02:49,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara will...</font>

43
00:02:58,939 --> 00:03:03,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought... I'd gotten over you...</font>

44
00:03:05,405 --> 00:03:07,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but if you're leaving my brother,
that changes things.</font>

45
00:03:08,505 --> 00:03:09,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

46
00:03:09,705 --> 00:03:13,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll make you mine and treat you well
our whole lives.</font>

47
00:03:14,305 --> 00:03:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

48
00:03:18,505 --> 00:03:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>No, no, no!</i></font>

49
00:03:19,572 --> 00:03:20,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not that!</font>

50
00:03:21,005 --> 00:03:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh no! What should I do?</font>

51
00:03:25,105 --> 00:03:26,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Yuri?</font>

52
00:03:26,972 --> 00:03:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's... kiss.</font>

53
00:03:29,705 --> 00:03:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

54
00:03:35,705 --> 00:03:36,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">SAKE</font>

55
00:03:37,205 --> 00:03:40,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I kiss anyone when I'm drunk.</font>

56
00:03:40,905 --> 00:03:42,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that what's happening?</font>

57
00:03:48,405 --> 00:03:51,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No... Wait, Yuri!</font>

58
00:03:52,105 --> 00:03:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri!</font>

59
00:03:53,105 --> 00:03:56,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really like you a lot,
but not in that way.</font>

60
00:03:57,005 --> 00:04:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a little soon for that,
I mean, it's going too far.</font>

61
00:04:03,305 --> 00:04:04,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

62
00:04:10,472 --> 00:04:12,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Ah! Ah! Ah! Eek!</font>

63
00:04:44,772 --> 00:04:46,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Five times on the cheeks.</font>

64
00:04:48,205 --> 00:04:50,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three times on the forehead.</font>

65
00:04:51,905 --> 00:04:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just barely covered my mouth.</font>

66
00:04:54,939 --> 00:04:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was close.</font>

67
00:04:57,205 --> 00:05:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How pitiful that my second kiss was also
in a strange twist of events.</font>

68
00:05:04,205 --> 00:05:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

69
00:05:07,005 --> 00:05:10,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, I'm really, really sorry
about yesterday.</font>

70
00:05:11,905 --> 00:05:14,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's totally all right, Yuri.</font>

71
00:05:15,605 --> 00:05:17,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wasn't I all over you last night?</font>

72
00:05:21,205 --> 00:05:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yikes!</font>

73
00:05:22,505 --> 00:05:25,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm seriously going to quit drinking.</font>

74
00:05:25,605 --> 00:05:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, if I try to have a drink,</font>

75
00:05:28,505 --> 00:05:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">knock me flat and bawl me out.</font>

76
00:05:31,605 --> 00:05:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Got it.
I'll knock you flat and bawl you out.</font>

77
00:05:34,405 --> 00:05:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. I'll need it.</font>

78
00:05:36,205 --> 00:05:37,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

79
00:05:40,171 --> 00:05:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There they are.</font>

80
00:05:41,605 --> 00:05:42,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. Uehara.</font>

81
00:05:46,105 --> 00:05:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Already in such a bad mood?
-Of course I am!</font>

82
00:05:48,772 --> 00:05:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come neither of you
have been answering your phones?</font>

83
00:05:51,905 --> 00:05:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It made me worry about you.</font>

84
00:05:55,105 --> 00:05:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're right. There's a lot...</font>

85
00:05:57,605 --> 00:05:59,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I turned my phone off.</font>

86
00:06:00,171 --> 00:06:03,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My brother's called you a bunch of times.</font>

87
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tell him that he doesn't have to.</font>

88
00:06:05,505 --> 00:06:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Tell him yourself.
-No way.</font>

89
00:06:07,305 --> 00:06:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

90
00:06:09,005 --> 00:06:11,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come here. I need to talk to you.</font>

91
00:06:11,105 --> 00:06:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine. See you later, Nao.</font>

92
00:06:16,672 --> 00:06:20,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri's taken off her wedding ring.</font>

93
00:06:22,872 --> 00:06:26,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao... Good morning.</font>

94
00:06:28,705 --> 00:06:29,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good morning.</font>

95
00:06:30,472 --> 00:06:34,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like you. I like you, Nao.</font>

96
00:06:38,805 --> 00:06:42,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Is that the woman Uehara likes?
-Ah! Ah!</font>

97
00:06:42,305 --> 00:06:46,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. Marina is waiting for me.</font>

98
00:06:46,105 --> 00:06:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She asked me to go over
the math problems with her.</font>

99
00:06:49,105 --> 00:06:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That stuff's hard, you know. Math is--</font>

100
00:06:51,705 --> 00:06:54,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Morning. What's is it?
-Come on. Come with me.</font>

101
00:06:54,105 --> 00:06:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Math is calling us.
-Huh? What do you mean?</font>

102
00:06:56,305 --> 00:06:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao!
-Yes?</font>

103
00:06:59,039 --> 00:07:01,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't have practice today,
so let's walk home together.</font>

104
00:07:02,039 --> 00:07:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry... but I can't go home
with you today.</font>

105
00:07:08,772 --> 00:07:10,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

106
00:07:12,672 --> 00:07:13,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm suspicious.</font>

107
00:07:14,005 --> 00:07:17,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When Nao panics like that,
it always means she's hiding something.</font>

108
00:07:19,105 --> 00:07:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm one reason she's panicking.</font>

109
00:07:22,572 --> 00:07:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

110
00:07:27,072 --> 00:07:28,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told her I liked her.</font>

111
00:07:32,939 --> 00:07:34,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

112
00:07:36,605 --> 00:07:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What... Hold on a second here.</font>

113
00:07:40,939 --> 00:07:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi told you he liked you?</font>

114
00:07:45,305 --> 00:07:46,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've got to be kidding.</font>

115
00:07:47,005 --> 00:07:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi is an old friend
and is like a big brother to her.</font>

116
00:07:49,305 --> 00:07:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That kind of thing can turn into love,
you know.</font>

117
00:07:52,305 --> 00:07:55,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really think so?</font>

118
00:07:55,672 --> 00:07:57,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just look at us.</font>

119
00:07:57,905 --> 00:08:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... that's right.</font>

120
00:08:02,205 --> 00:08:04,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what did you tell him?</font>

121
00:08:05,672 --> 00:08:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said, "I don't need an answer."</font>

122
00:08:08,305 --> 00:08:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I just wanted to tell you that."</font>

123
00:08:11,805 --> 00:08:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh... Daichi...</font>

124
00:08:14,772 --> 00:08:17,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can totally feel for him, right here.</font>

125
00:08:19,205 --> 00:08:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, you realize that Uehara's
not the only guy around, right?</font>

126
00:08:23,605 --> 00:08:26,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, you're not with anyone now,</font>

127
00:08:26,105 --> 00:08:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so maybe you should take Daichi seriously.</font>

128
00:08:28,972 --> 00:08:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But, for me, there's only--
<i>-Nao!</i></font>

129
00:08:36,605 --> 00:08:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

130
00:08:39,472 --> 00:08:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, I've got to go.</font>

131
00:08:45,305 --> 00:08:47,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's head over heels
with Uehara for sure.</font>

132
00:08:47,972 --> 00:08:51,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Uehara prefers Yuri, right?</font>

133
00:08:51,205 --> 00:08:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Probably.</font>

134
00:08:52,605 --> 00:08:55,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think Nao and Daichi
would be a great pair, don't you?</font>

135
00:08:56,472 --> 00:08:57,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess so.</font>

136
00:08:58,305 --> 00:09:01,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Any way you look at it,
Daichi is way kinder too.</font>

137
00:09:02,072 --> 00:09:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hmm...</font>

138
00:09:03,672 --> 00:09:05,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're going back to your home?</font>

139
00:09:05,705 --> 00:09:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah.
-What?</font>

140
00:09:08,505 --> 00:09:10,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But then, does that mean...</font>

141
00:09:10,305 --> 00:09:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you're never coming back
to our place again?</font>

142
00:09:12,505 --> 00:09:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Don't be stupid. Of course I am.
-Really?</font>

143
00:09:15,472 --> 00:09:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just until this mess
with Yuri gets straightened out.</font>

144
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

145
00:09:22,105 --> 00:09:25,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides,
it drives me nuts when she's there.</font>

146
00:09:25,972 --> 00:09:27,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd rather be at my house.</font>

147
00:09:30,405 --> 00:09:31,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it?</font>

148
00:09:33,672 --> 00:09:35,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing.</font>

149
00:09:36,105 --> 00:09:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did your brother say?</font>

150
00:09:37,705 --> 00:09:40,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said the affair is a misunderstanding,</font>

151
00:09:40,939 --> 00:09:42,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but something seems fishy.</font>

152
00:09:44,839 --> 00:09:46,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, I'm really sorry.</font>

153
00:09:46,205 --> 00:09:48,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Getting you involved
in my family's personal problems.</font>

154
00:09:49,105 --> 00:09:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't mind at all.
Besides, I really like Yuri.</font>

155
00:09:52,505 --> 00:09:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really glad to hear you say that.</font>

156
00:09:55,105 --> 00:09:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

157
00:09:57,205 --> 00:09:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, and I didn't make lunch today.</font>

158
00:09:59,939 --> 00:10:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK.
I'll just get something at the canteen.</font>

159
00:10:02,705 --> 00:10:03,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

160
00:10:08,672 --> 00:10:14,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"It drives me nuts... when Yuri's there."</font>

161
00:10:21,305 --> 00:10:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao!</i></font>

162
00:10:23,705 --> 00:10:24,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

163
00:10:24,805 --> 00:10:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's somewhere I'd like to take you.</font>

164
00:10:27,205 --> 00:10:28,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, but I think I told you this morn--</font>

165
00:10:28,939 --> 00:10:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, I've done a whole lot
of favors for you, Nao.</font>

166
00:10:34,205 --> 00:10:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, that's very true.</font>

167
00:10:36,072 --> 00:10:38,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Excellent. OK, let's go.
-Huh?</font>

168
00:10:40,805 --> 00:10:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

169
00:10:42,505 --> 00:10:44,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, kick it back.</font>

170
00:10:48,605 --> 00:10:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow!</font>

171
00:10:59,972 --> 00:11:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! It's the Sky Tree.</font>

172
00:11:05,705 --> 00:11:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's amazing!</font>

173
00:11:11,205 --> 00:11:13,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi, I didn't know you liked sweets.</font>

174
00:11:13,305 --> 00:11:15,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was in the mood...</font>

175
00:11:15,605 --> 00:11:17,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but just looking at it has made me full.</font>

176
00:11:17,939 --> 00:11:20,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're kidding. What a waste!</font>

177
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:23,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Then you have it, Nao.
-What?</font>

178
00:11:25,105 --> 00:11:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's OK. It's yours, Daichi.</font>

179
00:11:27,305 --> 00:11:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They say the sundaes here are so marvelous</font>

180
00:11:29,605 --> 00:11:32,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that you have to have at least one
before you die.</font>

181
00:11:38,605 --> 00:11:42,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! This really is delicious.</font>

182
00:11:47,005 --> 00:11:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. I'm sorry.</font>

183
00:11:49,605 --> 00:11:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This was yours, but look how much I had.</font>

184
00:11:52,905 --> 00:11:56,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I appreciate the concern,
but there's almost none left.</font>

185
00:11:59,405 --> 00:12:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're right. Hardly any...</font>

186
00:12:07,105 --> 00:12:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

187
00:12:14,705 --> 00:12:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have it, Daichi.</font>

188
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All right, if you insist.</font>

189
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's way too sweet.</font>

190
00:12:33,939 --> 00:12:35,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is Uehara there?</font>

191
00:12:37,305 --> 00:12:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... for a while,
he's going to be living at his home.</font>

192
00:12:41,605 --> 00:12:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really... That's good.</font>

193
00:12:49,672 --> 00:12:51,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi, I really like Ueha--</font>

194
00:12:51,605 --> 00:12:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

195
00:12:54,005 --> 00:12:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then--</font>

196
00:12:54,939 --> 00:12:57,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But doesn't he like that woman
from this morning?</font>

197
00:12:59,605 --> 00:13:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you not giving up on him
even though he likes someone else?</font>

198
00:13:04,839 --> 00:13:06,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't give up.</font>

199
00:13:07,572 --> 00:13:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I thought.
So I'm not giving up either.</font>

200
00:13:12,205 --> 00:13:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's different than--</font>

201
00:13:13,405 --> 00:13:14,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the same.</font>

202
00:13:16,405 --> 00:13:17,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Exactly the same.</font>

203
00:13:22,072 --> 00:13:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll wait for you patiently.</font>

204
00:13:24,505 --> 00:13:25,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Waiting is my specialty.</font>

205
00:13:27,672 --> 00:13:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, see you later.</font>

206
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

207
00:13:42,605 --> 00:13:44,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina.</font>

208
00:13:56,305 --> 00:13:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This all feels kind of weird.</font>

209
00:14:00,672 --> 00:14:03,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's like Daichi is different
than the Daichi that I know.</font>

210
00:14:05,305 --> 00:14:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

211
00:14:07,205 --> 00:14:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Either way,
I don't think Daichi is different,</font>

212
00:14:10,405 --> 00:14:14,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but now he's just serious about you.</font>

213
00:14:18,205 --> 00:14:20,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi says</font>

214
00:14:20,205 --> 00:14:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi will treat you way nicer
than Uehara will.</font>

215
00:14:24,839 --> 00:14:26,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not true!</font>

216
00:14:26,305 --> 00:14:28,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, I know Daichi is nice and kind.</font>

217
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Uehara is too.</font>

218
00:14:30,572 --> 00:14:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He bought me a cake on Christmas,</font>

219
00:14:32,705 --> 00:14:34,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and he came back home
during that blackout.</font>

220
00:14:37,705 --> 00:14:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll admit he says mean things,
and acts all big</font>

221
00:14:42,705 --> 00:14:48,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and is cruel and grump
and eats too much...</font>

222
00:14:48,072 --> 00:14:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?
It sounds like there are more negatives--</font>

223
00:14:50,405 --> 00:14:52,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But... But even so</font>

224
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:54,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">after living with him for two months,</font>

225
00:14:55,005 --> 00:14:58,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can swear with confidence
that he is nice and kind.</font>

226
00:15:00,305 --> 00:15:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

227
00:15:05,305 --> 00:15:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then I've made up my mind.</font>

228
00:15:07,205 --> 00:15:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

229
00:15:09,005 --> 00:15:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel bad for Daichi,</font>

230
00:15:11,205 --> 00:15:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I'm going to support you
in your romance with Uehara.</font>

231
00:15:15,572 --> 00:15:18,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Charge ahead down the path you've chosen.</font>

232
00:15:19,505 --> 00:15:21,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina...</font>

233
00:15:21,972 --> 00:15:22,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So</font>

234
00:15:22,939 --> 00:15:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">where is that special Uehara? At work?</font>

235
00:15:25,605 --> 00:15:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Where is he?</font>

236
00:15:31,972 --> 00:15:33,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, you see...</font>

237
00:15:35,305 --> 00:15:36,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

238
00:15:38,105 --> 00:15:40,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn you! With all the time
you've been spending together,</font>

239
00:15:41,005 --> 00:15:43,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">how come you didn't take action
right away?</font>

240
00:15:44,505 --> 00:15:49,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't help it.
The mood has never been right.</font>

241
00:15:49,905 --> 00:15:50,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah!</font>

242
00:15:50,839 --> 00:15:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You aren't trying hard enough!</font>

243
00:15:53,072 --> 00:15:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How hard do you think Mitsuishi
and I have been working at it?</font>

244
00:15:56,405 --> 00:16:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Unlike you, we're not living together,
you know.</font>

245
00:16:00,605 --> 00:16:01,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're right.</font>

246
00:16:02,905 --> 00:16:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara and I will be like you guys
in the future.</font>

247
00:16:05,972 --> 00:16:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're a little late in realizing that.</font>

248
00:16:13,105 --> 00:16:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hmm...</font>

249
00:16:23,872 --> 00:16:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to make sure our time
together is well spent.</font>

250
00:16:28,305 --> 00:16:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina sure is smart.</font>

251
00:16:33,039 --> 00:16:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm home.
-Oh, hi, Yuri.</font>

252
00:16:36,939 --> 00:16:41,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh? What's this? Tomorrow's lunch?
-Uh-huh.</font>

253
00:16:43,105 --> 00:16:44,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That seems like a lot.</font>

254
00:16:45,205 --> 00:16:46,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

255
00:16:47,205 --> 00:16:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! You're making one for Uehara too, huh?</font>

256
00:16:50,305 --> 00:16:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, uh...</font>

257
00:16:51,505 --> 00:16:55,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just happened to make a lot,
so I thought I'd make one for him too.</font>

258
00:16:55,972 --> 00:16:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought it'd be nice.</font>

259
00:16:59,205 --> 00:17:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see...</font>

260
00:17:04,405 --> 00:17:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara... Huh?</font>

261
00:17:09,305 --> 00:17:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

262
00:17:15,672 --> 00:17:17,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

263
00:17:17,705 --> 00:17:20,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've only got a limited time.</font>

264
00:17:20,171 --> 00:17:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go!</font>

265
00:17:22,972 --> 00:17:24,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's with you?
-Hurry!</font>

266
00:17:31,572 --> 00:17:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Aren't you going to eat?</font>

267
00:17:35,405 --> 00:17:36,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

268
00:17:38,605 --> 00:17:40,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My chest feels so warm.</font>

269
00:17:40,905 --> 00:17:43,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Heartburn? You must have eaten too much.</font>

270
00:17:44,839 --> 00:17:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't understand my feeling.</font>

271
00:17:47,939 --> 00:17:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>No, I'm sorry.</i></font>

272
00:17:54,505 --> 00:17:57,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Abe.
-This guy never learns.</font>

273
00:18:00,205 --> 00:18:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

274
00:18:02,505 --> 00:18:05,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no! I was so enjoying our time alone.</font>

275
00:18:05,405 --> 00:18:08,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, you won't believe this!</font>

276
00:18:08,205 --> 00:18:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you confess your love again?</font>

277
00:18:10,171 --> 00:18:12,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-And got turned down.
-Hey!</font>

278
00:18:12,972 --> 00:18:16,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll never understand how I feel,
Uehara.</font>

279
00:18:16,305 --> 00:18:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now, now. Cheer up, Abe.</font>

280
00:18:18,305 --> 00:18:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here, you can have my lunch.
-Really?</font>

281
00:18:20,705 --> 00:18:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uh-huh. Eat up.
-All right!</font>

282
00:18:22,505 --> 00:18:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go.</font>

283
00:18:24,039 --> 00:18:27,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It looks delicious. Thank you!
-No problem.</font>

284
00:18:27,672 --> 00:18:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Hey! What're you doing?</font>

285
00:18:29,705 --> 00:18:33,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-This won't be enough.
-How much can you eat?</font>

286
00:18:33,105 --> 00:18:34,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Enough for three.</font>

287
00:18:34,205 --> 00:18:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll make yourself sick
if you eat that much.</font>

288
00:18:36,205 --> 00:18:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm a growing boy, so don't worry.</font>

289
00:18:39,405 --> 00:18:41,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You skinny pig!</font>

290
00:18:41,305 --> 00:18:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

291
00:18:42,472 --> 00:18:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Like I said, you're a skinny pig.
-What are you talking about?</font>

292
00:18:49,705 --> 00:18:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. Tomorrow's Saturday.</font>

293
00:18:52,972 --> 00:18:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! If you need lunch
before your work tomorrow,</font>

294
00:18:56,905 --> 00:18:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll make you one, OK?</font>

295
00:18:58,305 --> 00:19:02,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You dummy. Tomorrow's a holiday.
Our foundation day.</font>

296
00:19:02,939 --> 00:19:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Uh-huh.</font>

297
00:19:06,472 --> 00:19:08,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then the next day we'll meet is...</font>

298
00:19:09,605 --> 00:19:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-In three days.
-You must be kidding...</font>

299
00:19:15,605 --> 00:19:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is the first time
since we've been living together</font>

300
00:19:18,905 --> 00:19:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that we won't see each other
for two whole days.</font>

301
00:19:20,905 --> 00:19:24,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Two days... That's a long time.</font>

302
00:19:26,472 --> 00:19:28,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not that long.</font>

303
00:19:28,305 --> 00:19:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, by the way, what are your plans
for the weekend?</font>

304
00:19:33,205 --> 00:19:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Work.</font>

305
00:19:34,505 --> 00:19:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. That's right.</font>

306
00:19:36,105 --> 00:19:37,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Later.</font>

307
00:19:37,605 --> 00:19:38,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

308
00:19:42,505 --> 00:19:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel like I'm always saying goodbye
to Uehara.</font>

309
00:20:06,872 --> 00:20:09,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He'd never text me.</font>

310
00:20:16,405 --> 00:20:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

311
00:20:19,472 --> 00:20:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri, your phone's ringing.</font>

312
00:20:22,305 --> 00:20:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

313
00:20:23,872 --> 00:20:26,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">HISASHI UEHARA</font>

314
00:20:27,605 --> 00:20:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks, Nao. They probably
want me to work on my day off.</font>

315
00:20:32,605 --> 00:20:35,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's Uehara.</font>

316
00:20:36,105 --> 00:20:37,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not again.</font>

317
00:20:47,939 --> 00:20:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish he'd call me.</font>

318
00:20:54,839 --> 00:20:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Here you go.
-Huh?</i></font>

319
00:20:56,905 --> 00:20:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Rolled cabbage, wieners,</i></font>

320
00:20:58,505 --> 00:21:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">clam chowder, hamburgers,</font>

321
00:21:00,305 --> 00:21:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">cars, computers, tako-yaki, tai-yaki..."</font>

322
00:21:03,972 --> 00:21:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">With these things,
you can capture Uehara's heart for sure.</font>

323
00:21:07,572 --> 00:21:09,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? All these?</font>

324
00:21:09,705 --> 00:21:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I've known him for a long time.</font>

325
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:17,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh. I wish I could return to that pure,
innocent time.</font>

326
00:21:18,072 --> 00:21:19,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean it's not like that now?</font>

327
00:21:20,205 --> 00:21:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Life's all messed up now.</font>

328
00:21:22,705 --> 00:21:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it was always just me
that was crazy in love.</font>

329
00:21:26,705 --> 00:21:28,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's never changed.</font>

330
00:21:29,305 --> 00:21:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? You mean with Takuya?</font>

331
00:21:31,772 --> 00:21:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.</font>

332
00:21:34,505 --> 00:21:36,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate to admit it</font>

333
00:21:37,572 --> 00:21:39,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he is really super handsome.</font>

334
00:21:40,505 --> 00:21:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">More than Uehara?</font>

335
00:21:41,772 --> 00:21:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep. They're like chalk and cheese.</font>

336
00:21:44,039 --> 00:21:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Uehara is chalk?</font>

337
00:21:46,305 --> 00:21:48,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep. Oh, I know!</font>

338
00:21:51,105 --> 00:21:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's probably got an old photo album.</font>

339
00:21:56,505 --> 00:21:59,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara will get angry if he finds out
you've been in his room.</font>

340
00:21:59,939 --> 00:22:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then let him get angry.
There's no need to worry about it.</font>

341
00:22:04,105 --> 00:22:07,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! What a nice bed.
Come have a seat on it, Nao.</font>

342
00:22:07,939 --> 00:22:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's OK.</font>

343
00:22:09,572 --> 00:22:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't be shy. Come on.</font>

344
00:22:12,772 --> 00:22:13,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not shy, just...</font>

345
00:22:15,305 --> 00:22:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think he doesn't mind if you do that,
Yuri.</font>

346
00:22:21,405 --> 00:22:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Excuse me.</font>

347
00:22:23,072 --> 00:22:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to do some shopping.</font>

348
00:22:25,305 --> 00:22:27,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Wait! Hold on a sec, Nao.</font>

349
00:22:39,105 --> 00:22:43,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder... what Uehara's doing now.</font>

350
00:22:54,105 --> 00:22:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ah! I'm sorry.
-No. It's my fault.</font>

351
00:22:56,805 --> 00:23:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, you were talking with Uehara
the other day. You're that...</font>

352
00:23:05,572 --> 00:23:06,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">pretty woman.</font>

353
00:23:07,005 --> 00:23:08,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you a friend of Uehara's?</font>

354
00:23:13,839 --> 00:23:15,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you are!</font>

355
00:23:15,072 --> 00:23:17,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It looks delicious! Yum!</font>

356
00:23:17,205 --> 00:23:18,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come here...</font>

357
00:23:19,939 --> 00:23:22,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've already got a new girlfriend?</font>

358
00:23:22,205 --> 00:23:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No...</font>

359
00:23:23,605 --> 00:23:26,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I'm getting my courage up
to ask her out.</font>

360
00:23:27,005 --> 00:23:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

361
00:23:29,305 --> 00:23:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Dad, one soft boiled egg!
-Here you go!</font>

362
00:23:34,472 --> 00:23:36,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Eat up. It'll give you courage.
On the house.</font>

363
00:23:36,605 --> 00:23:39,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, my teacher.</font>

364
00:23:39,305 --> 00:23:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-So...
-Yes?</font>

365
00:23:41,705 --> 00:23:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you friends with Nao too?</font>

366
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For sure. We're good friends.</font>

367
00:23:47,605 --> 00:23:49,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

368
00:23:49,705 --> 00:23:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then from your point of view,
what do you think of those two?</font>

369
00:23:54,939 --> 00:23:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I think?
I think they make a good couple.</font>

370
00:23:58,705 --> 00:24:00,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's because</font>

371
00:24:01,072 --> 00:24:04,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's working so hard at it,
don't you think?</font>

372
00:24:05,772 --> 00:24:06,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not really...</font>

373
00:24:06,905 --> 00:24:08,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Thank you!
-No problem</i></font>

374
00:24:09,039 --> 00:24:11,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey! What're you doing?
-This won't be enough.</font>

375
00:24:11,705 --> 00:24:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-How much can you eat?
-Enough for three.</font>

376
00:24:15,672 --> 00:24:18,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think that Uehara likes Nao too.</font>

377
00:24:20,005 --> 00:24:21,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? You think so?</font>

378
00:24:22,072 --> 00:24:23,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think so?</font>

379
00:24:31,005 --> 00:24:32,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you later, guys.</font>

380
00:24:32,405 --> 00:24:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

381
00:24:37,205 --> 00:24:40,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Daichi.</font>

382
00:24:41,405 --> 00:24:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! It's OK. I can carry those.</font>

383
00:24:44,305 --> 00:24:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure bought a lot.
Have you been worrying over Uehara?</font>

384
00:24:51,205 --> 00:24:52,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, not really...</font>

385
00:24:53,305 --> 00:24:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so easy to tell what you're thinking.</font>

386
00:24:57,905 --> 00:24:58,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think so?</font>

387
00:24:58,972 --> 00:25:00,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's what I like about you.</font>

388
00:25:06,705 --> 00:25:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait up.</font>

389
00:25:08,305 --> 00:25:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

390
00:25:12,305 --> 00:25:14,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Uehara.</font>

391
00:25:14,705 --> 00:25:17,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao! Uehara!</font>

392
00:25:17,105 --> 00:25:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yuri! Abe?
-Yo!</font>

393
00:25:20,572 --> 00:25:22,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You came back?</font>

394
00:25:22,605 --> 00:25:25,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just happened to be passing by,
that's all... Bye.</font>

395
00:25:27,039 --> 00:25:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have an idea!
Since Nao's friends are all here,</font>

396
00:25:30,839 --> 00:25:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">today we're going to have
a great big party!</font>

397
00:25:33,205 --> 00:25:34,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really? All right!
-Come on.</font>

398
00:25:35,005 --> 00:25:37,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell are you thinking?</font>

399
00:25:37,105 --> 00:25:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're worried, then you'll
just have to join us, won't you?</font>

400
00:25:39,572 --> 00:25:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

401
00:25:41,505 --> 00:25:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on, you two. Let's go.</font>

402
00:25:43,105 --> 00:25:45,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Come on. This way.</font>

403
00:25:50,305 --> 00:25:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since you insisted, we came.</font>

404
00:25:52,305 --> 00:25:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh! Welcome!
-Come on in!</font>

405
00:25:54,505 --> 00:25:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thanks for inviting us.
-No problem.</font>

406
00:25:56,672 --> 00:25:59,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll start by using these.</font>

407
00:26:02,105 --> 00:26:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go ahead.</font>

408
00:26:03,205 --> 00:26:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, OK.</font>

409
00:26:09,472 --> 00:26:10,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks, Mitsuishi.</font>

410
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Domino's Pizza.</i></font>

411
00:26:12,672 --> 00:26:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, the pizza's here.</font>

412
00:26:14,605 --> 00:26:17,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, handsome. You too, handsome.
Give me a hand.</font>

413
00:26:17,772 --> 00:26:20,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Me too?
-Did you hear? I'm handsome.</font>

414
00:26:20,205 --> 00:26:22,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-She said he's handsome.</font>

415
00:26:23,205 --> 00:26:24,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That'll go to his head for sure.</font>

416
00:26:24,872 --> 00:26:29,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow, I never thought you
and Uehara were living together, Nao.</font>

417
00:26:29,839 --> 00:26:32,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's like you've got a head start.</font>

418
00:26:35,872 --> 00:26:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, Abe, you've got to find yourself
a girlfriend first.</font>

419
00:26:39,605 --> 00:26:40,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.</font>

420
00:26:40,605 --> 00:26:43,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right now,
Yuri and I are really getting along.</font>

421
00:26:44,039 --> 00:26:46,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I'm going to confess my love
to her today.</font>

422
00:26:46,105 --> 00:26:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you thinking?
Yuri's married, you know.</font>

423
00:26:48,672 --> 00:26:50,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, forget that. Put out the plates.</font>

424
00:26:50,505 --> 00:26:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? What?</font>

425
00:26:52,872 --> 00:26:54,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, no. You're mistaken.</font>

426
00:26:56,605 --> 00:26:59,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I'm not mistaken at all.</font>

427
00:26:59,939 --> 00:27:02,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really? You're not?
-Never mind, Abe.</font>

428
00:27:02,405 --> 00:27:04,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Never mind?
-Never mind!</font>

429
00:27:05,805 --> 00:27:08,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, looks like we're ready. Shall we?</font>

430
00:27:09,005 --> 00:27:13,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uh-huh. One, two...
-Let's eat!</font>

431
00:27:15,305 --> 00:27:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This looks delicious.</font>

432
00:27:16,705 --> 00:27:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is all on me today,
so eat all you want.</font>

433
00:27:19,772 --> 00:27:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you!</font>

434
00:27:20,872 --> 00:27:24,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to eat until I burst!
Give me that fried chicken.</font>

435
00:27:25,472 --> 00:27:27,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know where to start.</font>

436
00:27:27,405 --> 00:27:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! This potato salad is delicious, Nao.</font>

437
00:27:29,805 --> 00:27:32,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? But I always start with--</font>

438
00:27:32,939 --> 00:27:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This, right?</font>

439
00:27:36,105 --> 00:27:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uh-huh.
-Here.</font>

440
00:27:39,005 --> 00:27:40,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

441
00:27:46,105 --> 00:27:48,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You dummy! You can't eat just meat.</font>

442
00:27:48,905 --> 00:27:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can eat whatever I like.</font>

443
00:27:52,872 --> 00:27:54,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

444
00:27:55,205 --> 00:27:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

445
00:27:56,939 --> 00:27:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No meat for you until you eat this.</font>

446
00:28:03,205 --> 00:28:04,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, Abe!
-Yes?</font>

447
00:28:04,672 --> 00:28:07,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you get me another drink?</font>

448
00:28:07,105 --> 00:28:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's already made me her gofer.</font>

449
00:28:10,405 --> 00:28:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What flavor do you want, Yuri?</font>

450
00:28:12,405 --> 00:28:13,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Orange.</font>

451
00:28:13,905 --> 00:28:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

452
00:28:15,205 --> 00:28:17,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, go get some dressing.</font>

453
00:28:17,105 --> 00:28:18,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go get it yourself.</font>

454
00:28:27,672 --> 00:28:29,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ORANGE <i>CHUHAI ALCOHOL 8%</i></font>

455
00:28:30,171 --> 00:28:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

456
00:28:38,939 --> 00:28:40,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh!</font>

457
00:28:45,039 --> 00:28:48,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dammit. Who let her drink alcohol?</font>

458
00:28:49,005 --> 00:28:51,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't touch me. It was you?</font>

459
00:28:51,072 --> 00:28:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah,</font>

460
00:28:52,305 --> 00:28:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I didn't know she'd end up like that.</font>

461
00:28:54,472 --> 00:28:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aah!</font>

462
00:28:56,772 --> 00:28:59,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe, I found you!</font>

463
00:28:59,872 --> 00:29:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get over here.</font>

464
00:29:02,305 --> 00:29:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let's kiss.
-Really? We can?</font>

465
00:29:04,405 --> 00:29:05,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes--</font>

466
00:29:07,705 --> 00:29:09,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so cruel to me, Uehara.</font>

467
00:29:09,939 --> 00:29:12,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Wait! Hold on!</font>

468
00:29:15,839 --> 00:29:17,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina, uh...</font>

469
00:29:17,072 --> 00:29:19,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Disappear, Mitsuishi!</font>

470
00:29:20,939 --> 00:29:23,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ow! You totally kicked me.
-Out of the way!</font>

471
00:29:23,705 --> 00:29:26,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ah! No, I couldn't.
-Daichi!</font>

472
00:29:27,005 --> 00:29:28,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Yuri!</font>

473
00:29:30,305 --> 00:29:31,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! That's mine.</font>

474
00:29:33,472 --> 00:29:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, OK.</font>

475
00:29:37,972 --> 00:29:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

476
00:29:48,305 --> 00:29:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't have anything
to do with him anymore.</font>

477
00:29:52,472 --> 00:29:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you see?</font>

478
00:29:53,705 --> 00:29:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm divorcing Takuya!</font>

479
00:30:02,105 --> 00:30:03,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Fine. Do what you like.</font>

480
00:30:07,505 --> 00:30:11,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry about that.
You young kids enjoy yourselves.</font>

481
00:30:11,605 --> 00:30:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The old person will now go get depressed.</font>

482
00:30:15,405 --> 00:30:19,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'll need your room, Nao.
-Hey, Yuri. Wait!</font>

483
00:30:29,205 --> 00:30:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I see...</i></font>

484
00:30:30,405 --> 00:30:33,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri's had a rough time, huh?</font>

485
00:30:33,105 --> 00:30:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

486
00:30:35,405 --> 00:30:39,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK, bye. See you.
-Yeah, see you.</font>

487
00:30:40,005 --> 00:30:41,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thanks for coming.
-No problem.</font>

488
00:30:41,972 --> 00:30:45,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh, adults sure do have it hard.</font>

489
00:30:46,505 --> 00:30:48,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got a bruise here for sure.</font>

490
00:31:07,605 --> 00:31:10,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri says she wants to talk to you.</font>

491
00:31:14,605 --> 00:31:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

492
00:31:20,805 --> 00:31:23,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It's Nao. Can I come in?</i></font>

493
00:31:24,939 --> 00:31:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

494
00:31:32,305 --> 00:31:35,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. I drank too much again.</font>

495
00:31:40,605 --> 00:31:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who was that call from?</font>

496
00:31:44,405 --> 00:31:45,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was Takuya's...</font>

497
00:31:47,505 --> 00:31:49,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">girlfriend from university.</font>

498
00:31:52,305 --> 00:31:56,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even since they broke up,
they've been seeing each other as friends.</font>

499
00:31:58,072 --> 00:32:02,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He even lied to me to go and see her
in the evening.</font>

500
00:32:05,105 --> 00:32:08,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh. I really hate myself.</font>

501
00:32:09,772 --> 00:32:12,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was always chasing after him.</font>

502
00:32:14,305 --> 00:32:16,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I must seem like a fool.</font>

503
00:32:19,605 --> 00:32:21,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think so.</font>

504
00:32:22,939 --> 00:32:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

505
00:32:27,672 --> 00:32:32,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think when you like someone,
you turn into a kind of fool.</font>

506
00:32:35,805 --> 00:32:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That person is always on your mind.</font>

507
00:32:40,305 --> 00:32:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You get upset over silly things
and worry about him for no reason.</font>

508
00:32:52,505 --> 00:32:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But when you're with him,
you're incredibly happy.</i></font>

509
00:32:57,805 --> 00:33:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All your troubles and worries
are instantly swept away.</font>

510
00:33:04,072 --> 00:33:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

511
00:33:06,505 --> 00:33:08,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, uh...</font>

512
00:33:09,005 --> 00:33:13,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, it's OK to be a fool, Yuri.</font>

513
00:33:13,939 --> 00:33:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

514
00:33:15,872 --> 00:33:19,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, I don't mean that kind of thing.</font>

515
00:33:20,039 --> 00:33:22,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... I don't know how to put it.</font>

516
00:33:22,605 --> 00:33:25,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Nao.</font>

517
00:33:27,305 --> 00:33:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure.</font>

518
00:33:42,005 --> 00:33:44,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is Yuri all right?</font>

519
00:33:46,505 --> 00:33:50,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah, maybe.
-"Maybe"?</font>

520
00:33:51,505 --> 00:33:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're that worried about her,
you go talk to her.</font>

521
00:33:55,205 --> 00:33:56,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This has nothing to do with you.</font>

522
00:33:57,805 --> 00:34:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me.
Sorry to interrupt you guys.</font>

523
00:34:01,305 --> 00:34:02,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-What?</font>

524
00:34:03,072 --> 00:34:04,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My stomach hurts.</font>

525
00:34:05,405 --> 00:34:06,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Huh?</font>

526
00:34:25,905 --> 00:34:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with that guy?</font>

527
00:34:28,405 --> 00:34:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think he overate.</font>

528
00:34:31,105 --> 00:34:34,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He'll be fine. He took medicine.</font>

529
00:34:34,105 --> 00:34:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So where the heck am I supposed to sleep?</font>

530
00:34:36,805 --> 00:34:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... Yuri's using my room too.</font>

531
00:34:42,605 --> 00:34:44,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll just have to sleep here tonight.</font>

532
00:34:46,305 --> 00:34:50,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You two...
You're going to sleep here together?</font>

533
00:35:07,572 --> 00:35:09,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're going to miss the last train.</font>

534
00:35:09,405 --> 00:35:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm staying over tonight.
-Huh?</font>

535
00:35:11,472 --> 00:35:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey, you crashed into me on purpose.
-No, it was just an accident.</font>

536
00:35:18,905 --> 00:35:22,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey! What are you doing?
-Oh, sorry. I didn't see you.</font>

537
00:36:07,005 --> 00:36:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So much happened that I can't sleep now.</font>

538
00:36:11,805 --> 00:36:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then how about something to eat?</font>

539
00:36:14,205 --> 00:36:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! You're awake, Uehara?</font>

540
00:36:17,405 --> 00:36:18,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

541
00:36:19,972 --> 00:36:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What's that?</font>

542
00:36:22,705 --> 00:36:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The one thing we both agree on.</font>

543
00:36:25,872 --> 00:36:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You got that for me?</font>

544
00:36:28,605 --> 00:36:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I just thought
you might want to have one.</font>

545
00:36:39,105 --> 00:36:42,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean you came here to see me today?</font>

546
00:36:43,205 --> 00:36:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What're you talking about?</font>

547
00:36:47,805 --> 00:36:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, nothing. Let's eat.</font>

548
00:36:53,472 --> 00:36:55,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you.
-Yeah, sure.</font>

549
00:37:02,705 --> 00:37:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! Dang, this is good.</font>

550
00:37:06,205 --> 00:37:07,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But a little warm.</font>

551
00:37:09,205 --> 00:37:13,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you think of milk pudding
when you think of me, huh?</font>

552
00:37:23,305 --> 00:37:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are all the smiles about?</font>

553
00:37:25,672 --> 00:37:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even though we've only been together
for a short time,</font>

554
00:37:28,705 --> 00:37:30,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we've already got this in common.</font>

555
00:37:31,039 --> 00:37:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

556
00:37:38,305 --> 00:37:40,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum!</font>

557
00:37:42,305 --> 00:37:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today, this pudding is better than usual.</font>

558
00:37:45,905 --> 00:37:47,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That doesn't make sense.</font>

559
00:37:47,672 --> 00:37:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because this is full of your kindness.</font>

560
00:37:51,839 --> 00:37:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you,
I just happened to be passing by.</font>

561
00:37:55,839 --> 00:37:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

562
00:37:57,605 --> 00:37:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, really.</font>

563
00:38:00,039 --> 00:38:03,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You going to eat that? I'll have it.</font>

564
00:38:03,105 --> 00:38:06,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You can't have it.
-Huh? Hey...</font>

565
00:38:07,572 --> 00:38:09,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Look.
-Huh?</font>

566
00:38:12,005 --> 00:38:14,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! This is so good.</font>

567
00:38:18,772 --> 00:38:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum. Pretty good, isn't it?</font>

568
00:38:36,305 --> 00:38:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh, what fine weather again today.
I'm feeling fine too.</font>

569
00:38:41,572 --> 00:38:43,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, then get out right now.</font>

570
00:38:43,605 --> 00:38:46,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Ah! Oh!</font>

571
00:38:46,705 --> 00:38:48,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez, you sure are cold to me.</font>

572
00:38:55,472 --> 00:38:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oops!</font>

573
00:39:05,305 --> 00:39:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh, now I'm all cold.</font>

574
00:39:10,839 --> 00:39:16,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, you're living at your house, right?
Let's go back together.</font>

575
00:39:18,072 --> 00:39:19,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to talk to you about something.</font>

576
00:39:22,405 --> 00:39:23,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, sure.</font>

577
00:39:33,105 --> 00:39:34,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did you want to talk about?</font>

578
00:39:34,705 --> 00:39:36,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You like Yuri, don't you?</font>

579
00:39:37,105 --> 00:39:38,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's none of your business--</font>

580
00:39:38,505 --> 00:39:42,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really don't care at all who you like.</font>

581
00:39:44,872 --> 00:39:47,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I will never stand for Nao
to get hurt by you.</font>

582
00:39:48,672 --> 00:39:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She and I aren't like that.</font>

583
00:39:50,039 --> 00:39:51,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why the hell...</font>

584
00:39:52,705 --> 00:39:55,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you tell her that?</font>

585
00:39:56,305 --> 00:39:58,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you dare take this lightly.</font>

586
00:40:06,305 --> 00:40:08,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've told Nao that I like her.</font>

587
00:41:11,605 --> 00:41:14,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nice to meet you. Thank you
for always looking after my brother.</font>

588
00:41:16,105 --> 00:41:17,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your brother?</font>

589
00:41:17,839 --> 00:41:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Uehara's older brother, Takuya.</font>

590
00:41:21,839 --> 00:41:23,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Older brother...</font>

591
00:41:27,105 --> 00:41:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! You're Uehara's big brother?</font>

592
00:42:51,505 --> 00:42:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
